<view class="index">
  <view class="index-bg">
    <image class="bg-image" src="/resources/images/halloween/bg_homepage.png"></image>
  </view>
  <view class="index-hd">
    <view class="index-desc">建立一个万圣节活动，随机安排一个朋友为你购买万圣节道具。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="btn-area">
    <image class="btn-img" src="{{buttonUrl}}"></image>
